Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}反恐24小时 第一季 第十五集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}恐怖份子正密谋 暗杀总统候选人\N(Jack) Right now, terrorists are plotting to assassinate a presidential candidate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我的妻女双双遭到绑架\Nmy wife and daughter are in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}而我的同事 可能同时牵涉这两件事\Nand people that l work with may be involved in both.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我是联邦探员杰克鲍尔\Nl'm FederalAgent Jack Bauer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}今天将是 我这辈子最长的一天\Nand this is the longest day ofmy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}以下是发生在 下午两点至三点的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}美国总统大选加州初选当天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我不容你这般无礼\Nl can go over your head, Mr Almeida.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}一切后果你自行负责\NAnd l assure you, there will be consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}对不起 可是我们得遵守规定\Nl apologise, Senator, but we do have protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们的主管查裴尔 正在准备您的通行证\NOur director, Ryan Chapelle, is working on a clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我会告诉他... -告诉他我要和鲍尔讲话\N- But if l could tell him why you're here... - All he needs to know is l need to see Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}而且是现在\NAnd l need to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}您等待的时候 是否需要...?\N- Can l get you anything while...? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我档不住他了 他要知道为何不能见杰克\NChapelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}l don't think l can stall him much longer. He wants to know why he can't see Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你怎么回答?\NWhat did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我说还有些事情要处里\NWell, l told him you were workin' on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-他还是没有说明来意 -没有，他只说要见杰克\N- And he still didn't say why he was here? - No. He just wants to see Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}没有进一步资讯 不能让他们俩见面\NWell, until l know more, l don't wanna put those two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我再查一查\N- l'm checking it out now. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-查出派默为何来这里了吗? -还没有\N- So? You find out what Palmer's doin' here? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-其他的杀手相关情报呢? -有一个，叫艾力西斯杜瑞森\N- Any new intel on the backup shooters? - Yeah, uh, an Alexis Drazen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}看来他与另两名杀手有关 但周六到达洛杉矶前\NLooks like he's connected to two other shooters, but he stopped in DC for two days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他曾在华盛顿 停留了两天\Nbefore landing in LAX on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}还有些疑点 我要查清楚\NThere's other inconsistencies. l'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-报告呢? -送到妮娜的电脑了\N- Where's the report? - l routed it to Nina's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}也给我一份\N- Send me a copy, would ya? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们不是该到杰克的办公室 去回答一些问题的吗?\NWeren't we supposed to answer some questions at Jack's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-到安全地点就会做 -我爸会到那里去吗?\N- We're gonna do that at the safe house now. - ls my dad gonna be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}还不会 可能等他离开反恐小组\NNot right away. Maybe when he's done at CTU.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-妮娜，一切可好? -一切都好\N- Are we OK, Nina? - Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}受监控的环境 对你们是最安全的\NA small, controlled environment is the most secure place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-杰克知道我们要去的地方吗? -当然了\N- Does Jack know you're taking us? - Of course. Myers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们要把泰莉和琴送到 安全地点，快到了\NWe're moving Teri and Kim to the safe house now. We should be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}妈，你都不讲 医生说了什么\NMom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}you never told me what the doctor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(Nina) No, l'm not worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}有个囊泡爆裂了\Nlt was a cyst that burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她说不严重\NShe said it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}没什么大不了的\N- Then why did she...? - There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她说这自己会好\NShe said it would go away all by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}甘恩斯曾打电话给我\NGaines first contacted me on my cellphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}叫我走到一部 停在圣马克医院旁车子\Ndirecting me to a car parked at St Mark's Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-车子里面有收发器吗? -有，他要我戴在耳朵里\N- The transmitter was in the car? - That's when he asked me to put it in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}可以帮我查查 我老婆女儿在医院的情形吗\NCan we take a break? Could you find out how my wife and daughter are doing at the clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她们已经离开了\N- Teri and Kim have already left the clinic. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她们很好 妮娜要她们到安全地点\NThey're fine. Nina's moving them to a safe house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你知道她们要被送走了 却不告诉我\NYou knew they were moving my wife and daughter and you didn't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}够了，我不讲了\NThat's it. This is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我一个字也不说了 让我跟查裴尔讲话\Nl don't say another word. l wanna speak to Chapelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}就是现在\NNow, Alberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你太累了\NYou're exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}昨晚接到你电话 真叫我吃惊\Nl was surprised you called last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我以为华盛顿那次后 我们不会再见\Nl didn't think l'd see you again after DC.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我可没那么容易甩掉\Nl'm not really that easy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你还会再休假吗\NWill you have another break later in the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}参议员今天下午就要走了 要到内华达州去\NThe senator has to leave town this afternoon, and he's going to... Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}只有我们几个人知道而已 我是其中必须跟随的人之一\NOnly a few of us were told about it, and l am one of the ones who has to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你得紧紧跟着他吗? -可以这么说\N- You have to hold his hand? - ln so many words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}到了内华达你会有空吗?\NWould it be too much to hope that you might have some free time in Nevada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你想一起去吗?\NYou would wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}要是你让我去的话\Nlf you want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}浴室很大 两个人可以一起洗\NThis is a pretty big shower. There's room enough for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我马上就过来\Nl'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我可以为你做什么吗?\N- Alan. - Senator Palmer, what can l do foryou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我想要跟反恐小组 一个叫杰克鲍尔的人讲话\Nl'm trying to talk to a CTU agent named Jack Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你在哪里? -在反恐小组，洛杉矶\N- Where are you? - CTU, Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他们说要有证件 但是我已经等得太久了\NThey say l need clearance, but it's taking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-那里是谁在做主的? -雷恩查裴尔\N- Not a problem. Who's in charge over there? - Ryan Chapelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我马上处里\NYeah. OK, l'll take care ofthis right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谢谢，亚伦 算我欠你的\NThank you, Alan. l owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}参议员派默先生 我是雷恩查裴尔\NSenator Palmer, Ryan Chapelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}有什么问题吗? 我为何不能见探员鲍尔?\NWhat seems to be the problem, Ryan? Why can't l get in to see Agent Bauer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}当探员接受 内部侦讯的时候\NPlease forgive the wait. When an agent is under internal investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们有规定在问话结束之前 必须被隔离\Nprocedure is to keep him isolated until he's been fully interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这不是我规定的\Nlt's... really out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}要是我对你们的侦讯 会有帮助呢\NEven if l can help you with your investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}查裴尔先生，国防部 亚伦澳普提肯先生来电\NMr Chapelle? Alan Optican from the Pentagon's on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}对不起\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我是澳普提肯 国防部的人\N- Chapelle. - This is Optican, Department ofDefense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你要马上处里参议员 派默先生所有需要做的事情\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Senator Palmer is to be given carte blanche. Make sure he gets whatever he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-听懂了没? -当然，长官\N- Yes, sir. - Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Of course, sir. - Thankyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}马上带杰克鲍尔过来\NBring Jack Bauer down here right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谢谢你帮我 把繁文缛节都省掉了\NThanks... for helping me... cut through the red tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}把所有摄影和录音设备 都关掉\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}l want all your cameras and recording equipment shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我要私下与他谈谈\NThis is going to be a private conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我了解，我会确保 这房间不受打扰\Nl understand. l'll make sure the room is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Hey, Jack. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}妮娜来电 说泰莉和琴都很好\NListen, Nina called and wanted me to tell you that Teri and Kim are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-谁负责那里的安全 -保罗森与布瑞赫\N- Who's guardin' the house? - Paulson and Breeher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}查裴尔找你 到会议室里去\NOK, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Also, Chapelle wants to see you in the conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}东尼，谢谢\N- Thanks a lot, Tony. - You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}抱歉我把那张卡片调包了 我别无选择\NMilo, l'm sorry l had to switch the cards on you last night. l had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们了解你的处境\NWe understand what you were goin' through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谢谢帮忙\NThanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Senator Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你走吧\NLeave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我会在外面\N- l'll be outside. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}关门\NClose the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}坐\NSit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我想知道 你和谁一夥的\Nl wanna know who's working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-长官，什么意思? -不必多说\N- ln which context, sir? l'm sorry, l don't... - Right here, right now. We're gonna end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我不懂你想要... -我知道你为何要杀我\N- l don't know what they told you... - l know why you want me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我听不懂你的意思\N- l don't know what you're talking about. - Kosovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}科索沃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:09:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我知道到今天你仍怀恨 我在两年前让你的属下牺牲了\N- Kosovo? - l know you hold me responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:09:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}for the men you lost there two years ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你知道有关暗夜计画的事? -那是我授权的任务\N- You know about Operation Nightfall? - l authorised the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我知道你攻入了维克多杜瑞森 内部，而且六个下属都阵亡了\Nl know you took out Victor Drazen and his inner circle. And lost six men in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}所以你以为我要报仇?\N- And you think l want revenge? - Yes, l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}今天我为了保护你 差点没命\NWith all due respect, l almost died today trying to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我的人在科索夫阵亡 都怪我自己\NAnd if l blame anyone for the death of my men in Kosovo, l blame myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那你今天在发电厂做什么?\N- What were you doin' at the power plant? - l was trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我会去抢那探员的枪\NThe reason l went for that agent's gun, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}是因为我得在保全自己的情况下 让你安全的离开那里\Nwas to try and get you out of the room without giving myself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}想要杀你的人 绑架了我的家人\NThe people that want you dead had kidnapped my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他们威胁我协助暗杀 不然就要杀害她们\NThey threatened to kill them if l didn't assist them in the assassination attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你到这边来他们没有 告诉过你这些事情对不对\NThey didn't tell you any of this when you came in, did they, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}是真的 你去问问查裴尔\Nlt's the truth. You can verify it with Chapelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她们刚刚抵达安全地点了\N- OK, they're just arriving at the safe house. - (man) Copy that. Show visual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}This way, Mrs Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这是探员保罗森与布里赫 他们与杰克共事多年\NThese are Agents Paulson and Breeher. They've worked with Jack for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这是杰克的太太泰莉 女儿琴\N- This is Jack's wife, Teri, and daughter, Kim. - (Kim) Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Hi, Kim. Where do you want us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我们要到哪里部署? -一个在里、一个在外\NOne in and one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这里不像是个家 但是也蛮舒服的\NWell, it's not exactly home, but it's relatively comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}每隔三十 就有个探测器\NThere are motion detectors every ten yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我们要在这里住多久? -等我们问话完毕再讨论这个了\N- How long do we have to stay here? - We'll worry about that after we debrief you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-浴室在哪里? -每个房间里都有\N- Nina, where's the bathroom? - There's one in each bedroom, through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}开始前你们俩 可能想先洗个澡\Nlf you'd both like to clean up before we get started, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}验孕片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}当时我是参议院中 特别国防委员会的主委\Nl was the head of the Special Defense Appropriations Committee in the Senate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那其实就是 偷袭行动的代名词\Nwhich is just a euphemism for covert operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}三年前中情局 向我提报一件事\NThree years ago, the ClA brought to my attention
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}就是科索沃的 维克多杜瑞森所犯下的暴行\Natrocities committed by Victor Drazen in Kosovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}屠杀，酷刑，种族屠杀\NMassacres, torture, ethnic cleansing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他简直是个禽兽 却逐渐受到支持\NThe man was a monster, and was gaining support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我透过正常管道干预 配合的速度却很缓慢\Nl tried to go through the usual channels, but l couldn't get anyone to work quickly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}结果我找了一个我知道 可以把事情办好的人去完成\NSo l contacted the one person l knew who could get the job done,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}先把他停职\Nhave him terminated, off the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-就是罗伯艾里斯 -没错\N- And that would be Robert Ellis. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}艾里斯透过 我的委员会资助\NEllis was funded through a discretionary fund of my committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他的工作就是偷袭行动 并确保不会有人知道是谁干的\NHis job was to implement the covert missions and see to it that no names were leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}所以我们俩 现在都是别人的目标\NNow we're both on somebody's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这就是 那天的结果要反扑了\NSo this is payback for what happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这样的道理才说的过去\Nlt's the only thing that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}要是有人 会把我们俩的名字放在一起\NBut if someone could put your name and my name on a list together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那他应该也会把 罗伯艾里斯放进来\Nthat means they should be able to find Robert Ellis, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你说的对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}4个6\NFour sixes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}翻开吧\NLet's see 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我知道 看你的眼睛我就知道了\Nl knew it! l saw it in your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你要真的看我眼睛就知道一切 你会爬到大石头下去大哭一场的\Nlf you could read what's in my eyes, you'd crawl under a rock and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}再来一次\NGo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(phone rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}巴比，我是大卫派默\N- Ellis. - Bobby, it's David Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-开什么玩笑 -不开玩笑，我在杰克鲍尔旁边\N- You gotta be kidding. - l'm not. l'm here with Jack Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你滚开\NGet lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}在鲍尔旁边?我一直很努力的 不想让你们俩认识\NWhat are you doin' with Bauer? l went to a lot of trouble to make sure you two never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}但是维克多杜瑞森里面的人 还是把我们连在一起了\NSomeone close to Victor Drazen seems to have connected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-讲清楚一点 -有人要杀我\N- Explain. - Someone wants me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}看起来也不放过鲍尔 就在今天\NAnd it appears they want Bauer, too. Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}暗夜行动刚满两周年\NThe two-year anniversary of Nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我是唯一知道 你们俩有关联的人\Nl'm the only one who knows you both were involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不会吧，若我们俩都在名单上 你也不会被漏掉\NApparently not. And if we're on the list, it's likely you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-让我跟鲍尔讲话 -巴比请讲\N- Let me talk to Bauer. - l'm right here, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杰克 你还在反恐小组吗\N- Jack. You still at CTU? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们得互相帮助 好找出凶手\NTo source this we need each other's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}很不幸的，过去的12小时内 我要作些牺牲\NUnfortunately, over the last 12 hours, l've had to cut a few corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}现在我被侦讯 乖乖就范\Nl'm being investigated right now. My hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}叫他们放了你 大卫会帮你的\NWell, get them untied. David can help you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}可能是你的人 之中最有嫌疑...\Nlt has to be someone either connected to your team...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我的人根本不知道 参议员的事\NNo. No one on my team knew of the senator's involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那就一定是 杜瑞森的人了\NWell, then it has to be Drazen's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我去调暗夜行动的资料 里面有杜瑞森相关的人名\Nl'll retrieve the closed file on Nightfall. lt'll contain the names of Drazen's associates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}目前你应该 要先查出那笔钱的来路\NThat'll take a few minutes. Meantime, you need to pick up a trail on the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}最有可能是从比利时来的 从你那里可以进入帐户查看吗\NOdds are it's funded through Belgium. Can you get to your K-3 accounts from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-要是我被复职就可以 -好，马上开始\N- Yes, if l get reinstated. - All right, start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}待会儿联络时我们对对看名字 我要怎么联络你\NWe'll compare names when we talk again. Where can l reach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}打到反恐小组 洛杉矶办公室找我\NCTU, Los Angeles office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(knock at door)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(Nina) Teri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Yes? - l put some clean clothes on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我在床上 放了些乾净的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他们说你不走了 我们不是要到内华达去的吗\NThey called me and said you decided not to fly out. Aren't we going to Nevada?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不去了，参议员有些事要处里 他认为这里是最安全的\NApparently not. The senator needed to do something. He thought we'd be safest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你会搭上下一班飞机吗? -希望会\N- Are you taking a later flight? - l don't know. l hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}回电给时代杂志，说我接受电访 只有45分钟\NCall the Times. Tell them l'll do that phoner, 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(dials out)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你想念我吗? -当然了\N- Hello. - You miss me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-不必去内华达了 -我正想订机票了\N- Of course. - l hope you didn't bookyour flight to Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}l was just about to. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-为什么 -可能会不去呀\NWe might not be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-几时可以知道呢? -再一个小时吧\N- When will you know? - ln about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}要是你留下来 你会留在饭店吗\Nlf you stay in town, will you remain at the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不知道 可能会换地方确保安全\Nl don't know. They might switch us for security reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我会告诉你 我在哪里的\NEither way, l'll let you know where l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我还闻得到 你的香水味呢\Nl can still smellyour perfume on my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我一确定就会告诉你\Nl'll call you as soon as l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}是那个女的吗\N- ls that the girl? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}派默可能 根本就不离开\NPalmer might not be leaving after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这样比较好\N- Better for us. - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}除掉甘恩斯的人 有什么问题吗?\NWas there any problem getting rid of Gaines's people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}根本就不该用他的 早就说过这样大错特错\NYou should never have used him. l told you it was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好，你来弭补 现在行动吧\NFine. You fixed the mistake, now let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(girl giggles)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她看起来好像玛提娜\NShe looks like Martina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}安德里，妹妹已经死了\NOur sister's dead, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不要再提了\NLeave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你找过霍凡和密斯科了吗? -他们正追踪着目标\N- Have you spoken to Jovan and Mishko? - They have their targets in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}派默这件事我答应你 午夜之前他死定了\NAnd as for Palmer, l give you my word he will be dead by midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-有牙膏吗? -在这里\N- Hey. Do you have any toothpaste? - Yeah, it's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这没什么 医生只是要我多小心一点\NThat's nothing. The doctor just wanted me to take it as a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}吓死我了\NYou scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Kim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你怀孕了\NYou're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我不懂，怎么会呢?\Nl don't understand. What happened today... How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}当然是跟爸爸，这种验孕 通常要受孕一段时间后...\Nlt was Dad, of course, but a test like this, it takes time before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你想再生个小孩 却没告诉过我?\NYou were trying to have a kid and didn't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不，亲爱的 事情不是这样的\NNo, honey, it wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Kim. Kim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- What? - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我和你一样非常震惊\NThis is just as much a shock to me as it is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们都有在避孕 虽然也不一定完全有效\NDad and l use birth control. lt's protection, but it's never 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你不需要我答应\NWhatever. You don't need my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我不是要你答应\Nl'm not asking for your permission, Kimberly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}有时候 你得体谅别人所经历的\NOnce in a while, you have to think about what another person is going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我刚发现我怀孕了\NHoney, l just found out l'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}难道我不会害怕吗?\NYou don't think that terrifies me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}会的\NWell, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}对不起\Nl'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这名单上 有你认识的名字吗\N(Ellis) Are there any other names on the HK list thatyou recognise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-里奇果恩，麦可瑞德门 -他们在行动结束前仍有嫌疑\N- Rich Goen, Michael Redman. That's it. - No, they weren't cleared until after the op.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-现在有什么我们就用什么 -我不该来的\N- l'll use what we have so far. - l shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-葛琳要我做些事 -我已经取消了\N- Green's got me on priority. - l cleared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}巴比，他来了\N- OK, Bob, he's here. - Milo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你是谁? -不必管\N- Yeah. Who are you? - Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我看到你 把国防反间线路打开了\NAh, l see you opened some sockets up to Ml5.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你怎么知道这些 -不必管\N- How did you know that? - Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我得找出一些人名 我会帮你的\NWe're tryin' to hook up some names. l'm gonna help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你的登录名称和密码\NNow, what's your login lD and password?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}给他吧\NGive it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}登录名称是LFN\NThe login lD is LFN.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}密码fOOthill94022\NPassword's foothill 94022.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}密码是小写的\NLower case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}等一下\NOK, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}找到一部分的资料了\NOK, looks like we got some partial results.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-一部分? -还有其他部分不见了\N- Partial? - Yeah. Looks like there's something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}什么意思?\NWhat do you mean, Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}有些东西被拿掉了\NSomething's been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我来看看\Nl'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}麦罗，我先送一个档案 到你的伺服器\NMeanwhile, Milo, l'm gonna... l'm gonna send a file to your server.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你去列印出来 给杰克和大卫\NWhy don't you print out hard copies for Jack and David?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-好呀 -谢了，麦罗\N- Yeah. Sure. - Thanks, Milo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}送去了\NAll right, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我简直要饿得抓狂了\NFeels like l haven't eaten in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}感觉真好，对不对? 不必再害怕了\NFeels good, doesn't it? Not being afraid any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}妈，对不起 我以前好笨\Nl'm sorry, Mom, l was being really stupid before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你几时才要告诉爸爸?\NSo, when are you gonna tell Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你知道吗?\NYou know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}就是现在\NRight now. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(phone rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-反恐小组，我是艾尔梅达 -我是泰莉鲍尔\N- CTU. Almeida. - Hi, Tony, it's Teri Bauer calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-杰克在吗? -他在，可是非常的忙碌\N- Could l talk to Jack, please? - Hi, Teri. Actually, it's a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- He's... he's kinda busy right now. - Could you tell him to call? lt's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}可以请他回电吗? 重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好的\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我真想看看他会有什么反应 -有你在真好\N- l really want to hear his reaction. - l'm so lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Aw, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们必须开始问话 反恐小组很想知道你们的事情\NHi. Sorry, but we need to start the debrief. CTU's eager to find out what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们准备好了\N- We're ready, huh? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}泰莉，就先从你开始吧\N- Great. l'd like to start with just you, Teri. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.54,0:24:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我先到房间里去 -你应该休息一下\N- l think l'm gonna go to my room. - That's a good idea. You should try and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这只是标准程序 我们会把你录影下来\NThis is standard procedure. We're gonna put you on videotape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.77,0:24:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}( ''Clocks Grow Old'' by lAm Spoonbender)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.26,0:24:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(phone rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.51,0:25:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Yeah? - Hi, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.14,0:25:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.18,0:25:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你还好吗? -还好，只是有点流血\N- Kim. - Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.89,0:25:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Yeah. l just lost a little blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你得看医生 听起来不太好\NYou need to see a doctor. You don't sound good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我只需要休息几天就好 -去自首吧，可以去治疗\N- l just need a few days' rest. - Turn yourself in. You can get medical help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.02,0:25:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我会被逮捕的\NAnd l'll also get arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.52,0:25:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}是你帮我们脱逃的 我会告诉他们的\N- But you helped us escape. l'll tell them that. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.09,0:25:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不要向他们提到我\NDon't tell them anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我妈妈正接受问话 他们一定会问到你的\NWell, it's too late. My mom's already being questioned. They're gonna ask about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.86,0:25:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我是下一个 我不会说谎\Nl'm next. l can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.43,0:25:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好，不要说谎\NOK. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}告诉他们 我不知道是什么事情\NTell them that l didn't know anything about what was goin' on
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}而且我被丹威胁 他手上有枪\Nand that Dan threatened me, he had a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.21,0:25:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好，答应我你要来自首\NOK, but promise me you'll turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.51,0:25:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我得好好想一想，我不像你 我不是来自好家庭的\Nl gotta think this through. l'm not like you, Kim. l don't come from a good family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.35,0:26:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}司法制度 不会放过我的\N- System's not gonna give me a break. - lt's your only way out of this, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.08,0:26:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这是你唯一的路呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.59,0:26:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我带你到甘恩斯那儿 那是绑架\Nl brought you to Gaines. That's kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他们会送我去 坐牢一辈子的\NThey could put me in jail for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.94,0:26:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这些事情 与我参选毫无关联\NWhat's incredible is that none of this has anything to do with me running for president.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.81,0:26:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}与这次的初选也无关\Nlt has nothing to do with... the primary.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.31,0:26:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}更与我的肤色无关\Nlt has nothing to do with my being black.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.42,0:26:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这只是来自 对付维克多杜瑞森的复仇\Nlt's just revenge for taking out... Victor Drazen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.04,0:26:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.08,0:26:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(phone rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.93,0:26:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}大卫，是我\N- Hello. - David, it's Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.83,0:27:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-你回到饭店了吗 -对，你在哪里\N- Oh, hi. Are you back at the hotel? - Yes. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.66,0:27:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我在反恐小组 政府机关\Nl'm at CTU, a government agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.17,0:27:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}为什么?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.80,0:27:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我要处理一些事情 -怎么一回事?\N- There's some things l have to take care of. - David, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.51,0:27:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我在调查 是谁想要暗杀我\Nl'm trying to find out who's attempting to kill me, Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.51,0:27:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我得走了，在饭店等我\N- l've got to go. Wait for me at the hotel. OK? - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.44,0:27:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.18,0:27:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}事情怎么停不下来\NJust doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.85,0:27:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}对整件事我感到遗憾\Nl'm sorry this is happening to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.16,0:27:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你被拘留了\NYou've been detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.59,0:27:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你的家人也被绑架\NYour family's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.13,0:27:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}可是你却仍关心我\NAnd you're concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.27,0:27:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那是与选举无关的事 是我儿子的事情\NThat didn't have anything to do with the election. That was about my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.04,0:27:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他还好吗?\Nls he OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.61,0:28:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我今天才发现\Nl just realised today...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.78,0:28:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我经常都没有 陪在他身旁\Nthat l haven't always been there for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}更要命的是\NAnd what's killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他无时无刻 都支持着我\Nis that he's always been there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.22,0:28:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}当政治人物的儿子 很不容易\NBeing the son of a politician isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.12,0:28:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}当个儿子，或女儿\NBeing a son... or a daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.36,0:28:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}或是父亲\Nor a father...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.90,0:28:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}也都很不容易\Nnone of it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.30,0:28:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你太太和女儿都好吗?\NYour wife and daughter OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.57,0:28:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不知道\Nl don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.64,0:28:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}应该还好吧\Nl hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.85,0:29:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}放轻松 我只有几个问题\N- OK. Just try to be relaxed. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.42,0:29:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}l just have a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.65,0:29:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这是艾里斯传来的 我把它分为三部分\NThis just came in from Ellis. l organised it into three sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.16,0:29:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}第一部分是所有参照资料 接下来是暗夜计画的简要内容\NCross-references are in the first part. Then there's a summary of Operation Nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.99,0:29:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}比较不重要的细节 放在最后\NDetails that may not be important are at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-不见的资料有下落吗? -还没有\N- Any word on the missing file? - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.17,0:29:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好，谢谢你，麦罗\NOK, thanks, Milo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.10,0:29:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}驻利比亚大使 怎么也在上面?\NWhat is the Ambassador to Libya doing on this list?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.91,0:29:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}可能是把资助杜瑞森的钱 与政府的钱分开吧\NProbably kept Drazen's money separate from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.11,0:29:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们注意他一段时间\NWe've had our eye on him for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.91,0:29:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}有听过一个 瑞尼邦尼尔吗?\NDo you know a Rene Bonniere?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.55,0:29:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-那是谁? -他从北非来的\N- No. Who's he? - He's out of North Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.05,0:29:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}分区上级觉得 他想在美国进行恐怖活动\NA couple high-ups over at District thought he was trying to set up terrorist cells in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.09,0:29:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杰克，看第四页\NJack. Page four.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.70,0:29:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}第二段下面\NSecond paragraph down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.40,0:30:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杜瑞森的妻女 也在沙堡里\NDrazen's wife and daughter were in the bunker?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.10,0:30:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你知道这件事吗? 之前的报告没提到这件事\NDid you know about this? This wasn't in our initial report.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.21,0:30:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}她们被炸死了\NThey died in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.91,0:30:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}天哪\NMy God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.95,0:30:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这是以牙还牙 因为我们杀了杜瑞森一家人\NThis is an eye for an eye. We took out Drazen and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.48,0:30:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}现在他们想杀我家人\NNow someone wants mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.88,0:30:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}是谁 在保护你的家人?\NWho's in charge of protecting your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.72,0:30:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谁有权力 加派安全人员保护她们?\NJack! Who has the authority to add security to your wife and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.96,0:30:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}查裴尔\NChapelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.59,0:30:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-参议员有什么事? -马上去叫查裴尔先生\N- (woman) Yes, Senator? - Send in Mr Chapelle right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.77,0:30:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.30,0:30:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你没办法观察到 任何有关他们计画的一切吗?\NThere was nothing else you saw or heard that gave you a glimpse into their operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.60,0:30:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不 在我们面前他们不多说\NNo, that's it. They really didn't talk much in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谈谈关於那个叫瑞克的男孩 他帮了你吗?\N- Tell me about this boy Rick. He helped you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}怎么帮?\NHow?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.51,0:31:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}各种方法，最重要是他给我们 一把枪还帮我们逃跑\NWell, different ways, but mainly he gave us a gun and he helped us escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.78,0:31:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-他怎么会有枪的 -不知道\N- How'd he get a gun? - l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.28,0:31:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}知道他姓什么吗?\N- And you don't know his last name? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.62,0:31:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我想琴也不知道的 -她们怎么认识的?\N- l don't think Kimberly knows either. - How did she meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.02,0:31:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}透过她的朋友 珍娜约克\NThrough her friend, Janet York.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.52,0:31:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}大家都说 "等你女儿变成青少年\NEveryone used to say ''Wait until she's a teenager,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.43,0:31:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你就知道担心的滋味了"\Nyou'll finally understand the meaning of the word 'worry'.''
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.69,0:31:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我相信她会长大的 杰克说她头脑很清醒\Nl'm sure she'll grow out of it. Jack says she's basically a level-headed kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.63,0:31:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杰克会提到琴吗?\NJack talks about Kim?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.00,0:31:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}会说些平常的事情\NJust the usual stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我很吃惊，他的工作看来 总是严肃而且秘密\Nlt surprises me. Jack's work always seems so serious and secretive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.64,0:31:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}很难想像他坐在办公室 与你们谈论家里的事\Nlt's hard to picture him sitting around the office talking about his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.68,0:31:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}有时候中午 他想到些事情就会讲\NSometimes at lunch he'll bring up something if something's on his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.22,0:31:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你认为瑞克对 犯罪首脑甘恩斯了解吗\NSo, do you think Rick had the confidence of lra Gaines, the leader of the group?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.99,0:32:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这我也不清楚\Nl really couldn't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.36,0:32:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}妮娜 可以请问你个问题吗?\N- Nina, could l ask you a question? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.39,0:32:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我与杰克分居的时候\NWhen Jack and l were separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.36,0:32:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他有提到过我吗?\Ndid he ever talk about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.87,0:32:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杰克从来不谈 婚姻的事情\NJack never discussed his marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.14,0:32:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他只是有时候会提到琴\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.29,0:32:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Sometimes he would... talk about Kim,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.41,0:32:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.81,0:32:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们都知道 他正面临一些困难\NWe all knew he was going through a very hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.75,0:32:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}而且他非常想念你们俩\Nand that he missed you both very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.25,0:32:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}后来我们复合的时候 他提到过曾经与人交往过\NWhen Jack and l got back together again... he told me that he'd been with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.10,0:33:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我说我们分居这段时间的事情 我不会在乎的\Nl told him it didn't matter what l did, what he did... when we were apart -
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.27,0:33:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}重要的是 我们从新开始之后的事\Nthat was in the past. The only thing that mattered was what we did from that point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.18,0:33:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那个人就是你对不对?\Nlt was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.26,0:33:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Teri.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.25,0:33:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们下直升机的时候 我就知道了\Nl saw it... when we got off the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.22,0:33:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你看他的眼神不一样\Nl saw it when you looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.30,0:33:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}在你们分居后\NAfter you were separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.37,0:33:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}是的，我们有交往过\Nyes, we saw each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.37,0:33:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}但是也不太久，他觉得错了 所以他回到你身旁\NBut it didn't last long. He realised it was a mistake and he went back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.81,0:33:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你认为呢?\N- What about you? - What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.05,0:34:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你会认为他错了吗?\NDid you think it was a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.48,0:34:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你仍然和他上床吗?\N- Are you still sleeping with him? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.02,0:34:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Teri...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.55,0:34:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他回到你身边之前就结束了 是真的\Nit was over before he went back to you. That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.89,0:34:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我知道这时候 发现这一切你会很难过\NLook, l realise this is a terrible time for you to discover all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.26,0:34:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不然什么时候 才是好时候呢\NWhen do you think a good time would be, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.44,0:34:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}抱歉\Nl'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们必须把口供问完\Nlt's just we have to get through the rest of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.47,0:34:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我想休息一下\Nl need to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.25,0:34:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}五分钟后我们就要走了\NYeah, Mike, l know. We'll be leaving in about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.69,0:35:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不等艾里斯了 我要走了\Nl can't wait for Ellis. l've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.63,0:35:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他们不会让我在这里工作 技术上我仍是在被捕状态中\NSenator, they're not gonna let me continue to work here. l am technically still under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.50,0:35:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.62,0:35:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Ryan!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.70,0:35:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-参议员，有事吗? -听说你们逮捕了杰克\N- Yes, Senator? - l understand you have Jack under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.21,0:35:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我告诉参议员 我目前被拘留中\Nl told the senator l was being detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.88,0:35:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}眼前的危机比他可能 犯下的任何过错都更严重\NThere is an ongoing crisis that supersedes any charges that might be filed against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.11,0:35:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我要求你们 马上把他复职\N- But Senator... - l want him reinstated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.98,0:35:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}长官，你无权决定这个的\NSir, you don't have the authority to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.27,0:35:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Alberta, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.59,0:35:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}长官，您的要求恕无法从命 鲍尔的罪状是非常严重的\NSir, what you are asking isn't possible. The charges against Agent Bauer are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.99,0:35:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}要是我们不听证就让他复职 就是藐视整个单位的规定\NWe'd be in contempt of agency regulations if we reinstated him without a hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.96,0:35:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我不需要正式的复职\NRyan, you don't have to reinstate me. Not permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.93,0:35:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这里没有人 比我对整个状况更了解\NNobody here has as much information about this situation as l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.50,0:36:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}只要今天给我 暂时的身份就好了\NGive me provisional status till the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.44,0:36:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}之后你们还是可以拘留我\NThen you can take me back into custody, do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.91,0:36:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}好，杰克\NFine, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.35,0:36:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你在反恐小组之外进行 但是你得对我负责\NYou work the case out of CTU, but you answer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}参议员 祝您选举好运\NGood luck with your campaign, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.24,0:36:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.02,0:36:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}陪我一起走\NWalk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.09,0:36:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}特勤组要我离开加州 他们说这里不安全\NSecret Service wants me to leave the state. They say it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.37,0:36:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我也这么认为\NWell, l agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.80,0:36:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我很清楚杜瑞森的人都到了 而且他们今天就会行动\NThe one thing we know... is that Drazen's people are here, and they want us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.84,0:36:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}现在也快三点了 今天也过了一大半了\NAnd it's almost three o'clock now. The day is more than half over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.78,0:36:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我要留下来\Nl'm going to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.01,0:36:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}让我把他们引出来 再来好好对付他们\NLet's flush them out into the open and deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.31,0:36:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不然你我的家人们\NOtherwise you and l and our families
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.68,0:37:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}会是我们这辈子的遗憾\Nwill be looking over our shoulders for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.38,0:37:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我懂，我会找艾里斯 有消息会通知你\Nl understand. l'll follow up with Ellis. l'll keep you posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.35,0:37:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你知道如何找到我的\N- You know how to get in touch with me. - Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.66,0:37:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}对不起我误会了你\Nl'm sorry that l misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.20,0:37:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}谢谢你，参议员\NThank you, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.13,0:37:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.51,0:37:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我妈妈来到之前，没有人理我 我被关起来了\NBefore my mom came, nobody talked to me. They put me in the room, l was locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.21,0:37:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}那瑞克呢?\N- What about Rick? - Rick? What about Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.21,0:37:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-他是绑架你的人之一，是吗? -也不全然\N- Well, he was one of your kidnappers, right? - Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.18,0:37:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他与丹一起 把你交给甘恩斯的\Nl thought he and Dan brought you to Gaines?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.85,0:37:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}其实主要是丹 不是瑞克\NWell, it was mostly Dan. l mean, not Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.72,0:37:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}当他知道是什么事 他也吓了一大跳\Nl think he was actually just as surprised as we were about what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.92,0:37:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}真的吗?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.49,0:37:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}对 他一直都在跟丹吵架\NWell, yeah. He was fighting with Dan the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.23,0:38:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}他还帮助我们逃跑\NHe actually helped us escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.56,0:38:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}不要讲得太快\NHold on. Let's not get ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.25,0:38:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(phone rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.10,0:38:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}等一下\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.77,0:38:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我是麦尔 -哈罗，是我\N- Myers. - Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.87,0:38:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}查裴尔暂时让我复职 是派默要求的\NChapelle reinstated me to provisional status for the rest of the day, at Palmer's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.61,0:38:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-太好了 -那边情况如何?\N- That's great, Jack. - Yeah. How's everything going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.45,0:38:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}还好\N- Not bad. - Look, we're sending over two more teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.18,0:38:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我们还要另派两组人 看来泰莉与琴也是目标之一
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.32,0:38:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Why? - Looks like Teri and Kim were targets as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.79,0:38:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}但是不要让她们知道\NNina... this is not information they need to know, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.46,0:38:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-当然了 -我和泰莉讲个话\N- No, of course. - Good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.33,0:38:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Let me speak to Teri, OK? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.84,0:38:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Teri?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.80,0:38:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杰克打来的\Nlt's Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.14,0:39:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}嗨，亲爱的 你还好吗?\N- Hi, Jack. - Hey, sweetheart. You OK? How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我还可以\Nl'm OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.98,0:39:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-那么琴呢? -她很好\N- How's Kim? - She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.45,0:39:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}东尼说你有重要的事 要告诉我\NTony gave me a message that you wanted to tell me something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.78,0:39:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}没什么大不了的\NNo, it's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.15,0:39:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}真的吗? 听起来怪怪的\NAre you sure? You sound funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.76,0:39:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}没什么，只是...\Nlt's nothing, l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.29,0:39:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.99,0:39:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我好累\Nl'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.49,0:39:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}试着休息一下\NWhy don't you try and get some rest, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.43,0:39:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这房子里 你需要什么的话\NListen, if... if you need anything from the house, Nina will make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.30,0:39:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}妮娜会帮你找人去取的\N- someone can go and get it for you, OK? - Yeah, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.80,0:39:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}得走了，我爱你 我会再打电话给你\Nl've gotta go. l love you, OK? l'll call you as soon as l can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.81,0:39:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}OK. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.49,0:40:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我马上就回来\NMom!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.83,0:40:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}l'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.96,0:40:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-说了些什么? -我没告诉他\N- So, what did he say? - l didn't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-怎么不说? -时间不对\N- Why not? - lt wasn't the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.60,0:40:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你应该回去找妮娜 把话讲完\NYou should go back and finish with Nina, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.50,0:40:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}怎么了?\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}没有，我只是觉得你得回去 让妮娜把话问完\NNothing. l just think you should finish answering Nina's questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}(phone rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.78,0:40:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}杰克，我是巴比\NBauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.12,0:40:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}- Jack, it's Bob. - Hey, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.55,0:40:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}我又传了一些资料给麦罗 但是不见的资料还找不到\NYeah, l shot over a few more things to Milo, but l still can't locate the missin' file.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.82,0:40:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}-我帮得上忙吗? -给麦罗的资料够你试试看\N- How can l help? - l gave Milo enough to try it on your end.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.32,0:40:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}这些档案我越看越觉得 那些资料是故意被拿掉的\NThe more l look at this thing, the more l'm convinced the file was taken out deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.06,0:41:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}所以我认为 我们要找的东西就在里面\NWhich leads me to believe... it contains what we're lookin' for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.17,0:41:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}你猜得出来 档案是几时被偷的吗\NCan you give an estimate of when you think the file was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.50,0:41:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}还有哪些人 会有资格动这东西呢\NAlso a list of people you think could've had access to even get in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.24,0:41:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}还不知道，告诉麦罗 我找到一个方法...\NNot yet, but you tell Milo l got some ideas on how to...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.65,0:41:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Urgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.40,0:41:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.45,0:41:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.00,0:41:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.85,0:41:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}听得到吗?\NCan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.33,0:41:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\bord0}Bob?
